<br>
I think it is apparent from this thread that it is pointless to count on non-fatty warriors to bash casters if you run into trouble. Too many are of the opinion they can't bash worth a damn and can help more by continuing to smack the mob with their weapons. The majority will not be convinced otherwise no matter how hard an opposing viewpoint is argued. My advice is to make sure you have a chanter and a pally/sk in your group if you know you are facing casting mobs. <p>Gulor Gularin
